    <context>No architecture doc exists for the background workers subsystem. Multiple IHostedService implementations run alongside the BFF API: subscription renewal, cache warming, health monitors, scheduled tasks. This doc needs to be created from scratch by searching for and reading all IHostedService implementations.</context>
    <constraints>
      - Use /docs-architecture skill structure
